## Summary

**ATO** is a **mission-critical tax optimization SaaS** that integrates Xero accounting data, applies forensic AI analysis (Gemini), and runs 16 specialized tax engines to identify $200K–$500K in missed tax benefits per client. 

**Architecture Strengths:**
- ✅ Read-only Xero access eliminates risk
- ✅ RLS-enforced multi-tenant isolation
- ✅ 29 specialized agents coordinated via Linear
- ✅ 10 Python validators (90-95% confidence)
- ✅ Decimal.js prevents financial errors
- ✅ Monitoring agents (5) continuously check health

**Critical Liabilities:**
- ⚠️ **Single point of failure:** TaxDataCache (all engines depend on it)
- ⚠️ **Rate limit bottleneck:** Gemini API 15 req/min (free tier)
- ⚠️ **No distributed rate limiting:** In-memory only (not Vercel-safe)
- ⚠️ **No work queue:** Batch analyses run sequentially, no retries
- ⚠️ **Schema scaling:** `forensic_analysis_results` unpartitioned (1M+ rows will slow)

**Will break under load:** Concurrent syncs, large batches, cache expiry, Gemini rate limits.